window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Two sisters. Two loves. And a secret that can destroy them both.<br> <br> Since she was young, Silver has used her magic to draw a single human soul out from the afterlife. Though she shaped him into a wax raven, Keelen could never stay, so she brought him back time and time again. Each visit, their relationship deepened, leading Silver to want more than friendship. Yet it isn’t until after Silver and her queen sister, Afton, are forced to defend themselves from an enemy king's guards, that Silver discovers a way to give Keelen human life and become Afton’s weapon.<br> <br> Afton has never given her heart to anyone until she met Ragan. However, she must temporarily push her feelings aside and accept the betrothal to the enemy king to keep her territory safe. But when Afton uncovers a danger that threatens all she has built, it is only the sisters who can put a stop to it before everything they love, including their sisterly bond, shatters.<br> <br> Perfect for fans of Laini Taylor, Kerri Maniscalco, and Emma Hamm. <i>Merciless Stars</i> is an enticing stand-alone romantic fantasy. If you love sizzling romance, strong female leads, twists and turns, and magic, then this is one addicting book you won't want to miss!</p>"; 
